---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const mkPath = (path) => {
  const cleanBase = base.endsWith('/') ? base.slice(0, -1) : base;
  return `${cleanBase}${path.startsWith('/') ? path : '/' + path}`;
};
---

<Layout title="应用 - Moxin Org">

  <div class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse animate-fade-in">
      Moly <br />
      <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-pink to-purple-500">
        跨平台 LLM 客户端
      </span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 font-light">
      一个隐私优先、零配置的界面，适用于您所有的本地 LLM。支持 macOS、Windows 和 Linux。
    </p>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12 animate-fade-in relative z-10">
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-pink/10 to-purple-500/10 border border-accent-pink/20 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all cursor-pointer text-center transform hover:scale-105" onclick="window.open('https://moly-ai.ai', '_blank')">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse">访问 Moly 网站</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse mb-4 text-lg">一个隐私优先、零配置的界面，适用于您所有的本地 LLM。</p>
        <span class="text-accent-pink font-bold text-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          moly-ai.ai 
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg>
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>

      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-gray-50">
        <video class="w-full h-auto" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
          <source src={mkPath("/images/moly-chat-demo.DP8cZCTz.mov")} type="video/mp4">
          Your browser does not support the video tag.
        </video>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto mb-24">
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse">跨平台</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse leading-relaxed">
          使用 Rust 和 Makepad 构建，Moly 在 macOS、Linux 和 Windows 上原生运行。体验跨所有设备的无缝 AI 交互。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse">本地与远程 LLM</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse leading-relaxed">
          连接到 OpenAI、Anthropic，或使用 Moly Server 在本地运行模型。选择尖端的云模型或在本地运行开源模型。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse">闪电般快速</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse leading-relaxed">
          使用 Rust 构建，以实现最高性能和内存安全。体验即时响应、优化的内存使用和原生性能。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse">开源</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse leading-relaxed">
          完全开源，采用 Apache 2.0 许可证。加入我们的社区，为项目做出贡献，或构建您自己的 AI 驱动的应用程序。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse">隐私优先</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse leading-relaxed">
          通过本地模型实现完全的数据主权。云对话端到端加密。您的对话保持私密。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse">AI 智能体集成</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse leading-relaxed">
          连接到 MoFa 服务器以与 AI 智能体交互。部署自定义 AI 智能体并创建自动化工作流。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Section Removed -->
  </div>
</Layout>
